description:
Team Leader welcomes this perfect chance to secure this street front 485 sqm block in the sort after suburb of Beckenham. This large lot gives you opportunity to create, design & build your dream home.

Attracting young professionals, families or investors.

Beckenham, is located in The City of Gosnells has quickly become an emerging suburb due to its proximity to Perth CBD of a merely 15minutes by rail. Featuring the popular recreational facility at Mills Park and a short cycling distance to Canning River & Greater Brixton Street Wetlands. Just beyond the neighbourhood you will find newly revamped Westfield Carousel Shopping precinct, Curtin University & Beckenham Station where the City of Gosnells have some exciting plans to activate the area.

Reasons to love this block:
- Street front & green title
- 485 sqm vacant lot
- 48.28m depth, 10.06m frontage
- Titles in the process of getting issued (currently a proposed lot )
- Great size block to build your dream home or future investment
- Cleared and ready to build once titles are issued
- Located approx 20 minutes from Perth CBD


Contact Joshua 0432 183 369 from Team Leader The Agency for land inquiry information.
